'''李察·奧費安'''（{{lang-en|'''Richard Offiong'''}}，{{bd|1983年|12月17日|catIdx=Offiong, Richard}}），[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]。現時效力英格蘭北部足球聯賽球會[[达勒姆城足球俱乐部|杜倫城]]。

==生平==
奧費安於[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]青年隊展開其職業足球生涯，但未曾在一隊上陣。在紐卡素時期，奧費安曾入選英格蘭U20國家隊，曾被外借三次。2002年11月首次被外借，效力[[达灵顿足球俱乐部|達寧頓]]兩個月<small><ref name="Offiong agrees loan switch">{{cite news
| title = Offiong agrees loan switch
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/2530683.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2002-11-30
| accessdate = 2007-11-24}}{{en}}</ref><ref name="Offiong decision due">{{cite news
| title = Offiong decision due
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/2686737.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2003-01-23
| accessdate = 2007-11-24 }}{{en}}</ref></small>。達寧頓在2月決定不延續第三個月外借期<small><ref name="Offiong returns to Magpies">{{cite news
| title = Offiong returns to Magpies
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/2705425.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2003-02-13
| accessdate = 2007-11-24
| archive-date = 2004-07-11
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040711061816/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/2705425.stm
| dead-url = no
}}{{en}}</ref></small>，期間上陣9場射入4球<small><ref name="Richard Offiong">{{cite web
| title = Richard Offiong
| url = http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=34174
| publisher = Soccerbase
| accessdate = 2007-11-24
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070525025114/http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=34174
| archive-date = 2007-05-25
| dead-url = yes
}}{{en}}</ref></small>。

2003年1月他被外借至[[马瑟韦尔足球俱乐部|馬瑟韋爾]]<small><ref name="Well make double swoop">{{cite news
| title = Well make double swoop
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/motherwell/2714685.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2003-01-31
| accessdate = 2007-11-24
| archive-date = 2007-08-27
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070827214353/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/motherwell/2714685.stm
| dead-url = no
}}{{en}}</ref></small>，僅為球會9次後備上陣<small><ref name="Richard Offiong"/></small>。2004年3月他被外借至[[約克城足球會|約克城]]（York City）一個月，上陣4場<small><ref name="Richard Offiong"/><ref name="Brass makes double swoop">{{cite news
| title = Brass makes double swoop
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/y/york_city/3507720.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2004-03-13
| accessdate = 2007-11-24
| archive-date = 2004-04-08
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20040408010806/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/y/york_city/3507720.stm
| dead-url = no
}}{{en}}</ref></small>。球季季尾他離開紐卡素，在2004至05年期間他輾轉效力[[土耳其|土耳其]]、[[韓國|韓國]]和[[比利時|比利時]]的球會。奧費安回復自由身，免費加盟[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|唐卡士打]]，但只獲得5次上陣機會，終於季尾離隊。

2006年他加盟[[咸美顿学院足球俱乐部|咸美頓]]，於11月他和球會簽下合約，期限至2009年5月完結<small><ref name="Hamilton pair agree new contracts">{{cite news
| title = Hamilton pair agree new contracts
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/hamilton_academical/6111076.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2006-11-02
| accessdate = 2007-11-24 }}{{en}}</ref></small>。2007年8月他獲選該月最佳球員<small><ref name="Irn Bru rewards Reid and Offiong">{{cite news
| title = Irn Bru rewards Reid and Offiong
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/hamilton_academical/7007341.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2007-09-21
| accessdate = 2007-11-24 }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

2008年2月9日在新道格拉斯公園（New Douglas Park）對戰[[邓弗姆林足球俱乐部|鄧弗姆林]]首次大演帽子戲法，助球會大勝3-0，他在對這支前[[蘇超|蘇超]]球會3戰共射入5球。

2007/08年球季咸美頓幾經波折，終獲得[[蘇超|蘇超]]的席位。蘇超處子戰以3-1擊敗[[邓迪联足球俱乐部|登地聯]]，在球隊勝[[因弗内斯足球俱乐部|恩華尼斯]]1-0的賽事中，奧費安射入全場唯一入球，在蘇超聯賽「開齋」<small><ref name="Hamilton Accies 3-1 Dundee United">{{cite news
| title = Hamilton Accies 3-1 Dundee United
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/7550065.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2008-08-11
| accessdate = 2008-08-17 }}{{en}}</ref><ref name="Inverness CT 0-1 Hamilton Accies">{{cite news
| title = Inverness CT 0-1 Hamilton Accies
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/scot_prem/7561727.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2008-08-16
| accessdate = 2008-08-17 }}{{en}}</ref></small>。他在12月和咸美頓簽下新合約，至2009/10年球季季尾才完結<small><ref name="Offiong extends Accies contract">{{cite news
| title = Offiong extends Accies contract
| url = http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/hamilton_academical/7776266.stm
| publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] Sport
| date = 2008-12-10
| accessdate = 2008-12-10 }}{{en}}</ref></small>。

2009年夏季[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]球會[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|高車士打]]有意收購奧費安，但他沒有向新球會報到而取消交易<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/8163011.stm |title=Three heading for Colchester exit |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-07-22 |accessdate=2009-07-23 |archive-date=2019-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217170225/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/colchester_united/8163011.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。最終於8月25日轉投另一支英甲球隊[[卡莱尔联足球俱乐部|卡素爾]]，簽約兩年，可優先續約一年，轉會費75,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]，如球隊獲得升班將加至90,000英鎊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5513651,00.html |title=Carlisle seal Offiong move |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-08-25 |accessdate=2009-08-26 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308021838/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_5513651,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。惟奧費安一直無法融入球隊，直到2010年1月26日以3-2擊敗[[埃克塞特城足球俱乐部|艾斯特城]]，於補時射入致勝球兼加盟以來首個聯賽入球。在球隊無法掙到常規正選席位，於3月30日被外借到[[瑞典|瑞典]]第三級聯賽球隊[[厄斯特松德足球俱乐部|厄斯特松德]]15個星期<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_6063942,00.html |title=Offiong heads to Sweden |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-03-30 |accessdate=2010-04-01}}</ref></small>。借用期滿後奧費安返回卡素爾，但大腿卻有傷，直到8月初才復操，於2010年8月16日再被外借到剛降班[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽]]的[[达灵顿足球俱乐部|達寧頓]]一個月，爭取儘快恢復狀態<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/8917481.stm |title=Darlington sign Carlisle's Richard Offiong on loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-16 |accessdate=2010-08-17 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307080627/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/8917481.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。但奧費安始終未能回復狀態，於2011年1月4日與卡素爾雙方同意提前解約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/9337901.stm |title=Carlisle part company with striker Richard Offiong |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-04 |accessdate=2011-01-05 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307022547/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/carlisle_united/9337901.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

